wo Lakes-Matt Rosner']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Ftwo-lakes%252Fid387448101%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Two Lakes-Matt Rosner']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/kaleidoscope.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/kaleidoscope.jpg" alt="Kaleidoscope / Susumu Yokota" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/kaleidoscope.php">Kaleidoscope<br />Susumu Yokota</a></h4><p>まるでどこか違う国へトリップしてしまったような気分になれる音楽。移動の飛行機や車中で聴きながら過ごせば海外旅行をしているような気分になれるかもしれません。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B003X5ODCK?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B003X5ODCK" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Kaleidoscope-Susumu Yokota']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/model-3-step-2.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/model3.jpg" alt="Model 3, Step 2 / Microstoria" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/model-3-step-2.php">Model 3, Step 2<br />Microstoria</a></h4><p>アコースティックとエレクトリックの2つの要素が絶妙なバランスで交わっていく作品。朝起きたときや寝る前に聴きたくなるような音楽です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B00005212P?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B00005212P" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Model 3, Step 2-Microstoria']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fmodel-3-step-2%252Fid5509727%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Model 3, Step 2-Microstoria']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/thrill130.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/so.jpg" alt="Thrill130 / So" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/thrill130.php">Thrill130<br />So</a></h4><p>ホテルの部屋などで無音が寂しいとき、または耳にうるさい音楽を聴きたくないときなどに活躍する作品です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0000B17QV?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0000B17QV" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Thrill130-So']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fso%252Fid5510817%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Thrill130-So']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/dok.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/dok.jpg" alt="Dok / Oval" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/dok.php">Dok<br />Oval</a></h4><p>移動も終えて疲れたときや、宿泊先で就寝するときなどにこの音楽は合います。心地よい子守唄でゆったりと優雅に眠りましょう。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000004B3G?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000004B3G" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Dok-Oval']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fdok%252Fid5507109%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Dok-Oval']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/field-recordings-19952002.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/fieldrecordings.jpg" alt="Field Recordings 1995:2002 / Fennesz" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/field-recordings-19952002.php">Field Recordings 1995:2002<br />Fennesz</a></h4><p>朝起きて気合いを入れたいとき、じっくりと気分を盛り上げていきたいときなどにおすすめの作品です。心地よい音響が特徴の作品です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0000789WQ?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0000789WQ" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Field Recordings 1995:2002-Fennesz']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Ffield-recordings-1995-2002%252Fid77798046%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Field Recordings 1995:2002-Fennesz']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div></div>

